subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Logano secured the first berth in the next round of the Chase for the Sprint Cup, Nascar’s championship playoffs, with a victory at Kansas Speedway.
